foia:ProcessedRequestComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: Although VA indicated in its FY 2014 Annual Report a different number then above, the figure denoted in this chart is correct. The difference is attributed to the following: 1) in some instances the office did not show requests that were in fact completed in FY 2014 as completed in VA’s FOIA tracking system until after the FY 2014 report was finalized.

foia:BackloggedRequestComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: Although VA indicated in its FY 2014 Annual Report a different number then above, the figure denoted in this chart is correct. The difference is attributed to the following: 1) in some instances the office did not show requests that were in fact completed in FY 2014 as compleded in VA's FOIA tracking system until after the FY 2014 report was finalized, and 2) due to an organizational restructuring in which requests for claim files were centralized at one location within VBA while regional offices previously responsible for processing claim files transitioned out of this task and requests were not timely entered into our tracking system.
